&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>Powerline in WSL2</title><link>/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 Oct 2021 16:19:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/</guid><description>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02.png" alt="Featured image of post Powerline in WSL2" />&lt;p>在wsl2中使用zsh主题出现乱码时需要安装powerline字体才能显示，windows terminal使用的Cascadia Code字体也支持powerline版本
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code#installation"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Cascadia Code&lt;/a>
，常用的还有
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/powerline/fonts"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>powerline/fonts&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对于Cascadia Code字体下载
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code/releases"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>microsoft/cascadia-code/releases&lt;/a>
解压安装即可：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02.png"
width="836"
height="385"
srcset="/posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02_hu_4005b900ffdf5d0b.png 480w, /posts/2021/10/powerline-in-wsl2/2021-10-17-20-09-02_hu_c0c55995f2f387dc.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="217"
data-flex-basis="521px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对于powerline字体文件可以使用&lt;code>git clone https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git --depth=1&lt;/code>下载后在管理员权限下执行安装
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/powerline/fonts/blob/master/install.ps1"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>install.ps1&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="配置使用">配置使用
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>vscode：在settings.json中添加&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;terminal.integrated.fontFamily&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Cascadia Mono PL&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>windows terminal：在settings.json中添加&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;profiles&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;defaults&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;fontFace&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Cascadia Code PL&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> },
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/terminal/tutorials/powerline-setup"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Tutorial: Set up Powerline in Windows Terminal&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/editor/integrated-terminal#_can-i-use-powerline-fonts-in-the-integrated-terminal"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Can I use Powerline fonts in the integrated terminal?&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>docker installation</title><link>/posts/archives/docker/docker-installation/</link><pubDate>Fri, 06 Aug 2021 17:30:53 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/archives/docker/docker-installation/</guid><description>&lt;p>在
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Install Docker Engine on Ubuntu&lt;/a>
提供了安装教程，同时提供一个直接运行的脚本
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/#install-using-the-convenience-script"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Install using the convenience script&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com -o get-docker.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo sh get-docker.sh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="manage-docker-as-a-non-root-user">Manage Docker as a non-root user
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在安装完成后不能使用非root用户运行，可能遇到下面的问题：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ docker stats
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Got permission denied &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">while&lt;/span> trying to connect to the Docker daemon socket at unix:///var/run/docker.sock: Get &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;http://%2Fvar%2Frun%2Fdocker.sock/v1.24/version&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: dial unix /var/run/docker.sock: connect: permission denied
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>可以为当前用户添加到docker组中解决&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo groupadd docker
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo usermod -aG docker &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>$USER&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Change user&amp;#39;s primary group membership or logout and login again or reboot&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>newgrp docker
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="rootless-mode">Rootless mode
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>在
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://docs.docker.com/engine/security/rootless/#install"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Run the Docker daemon as a non-root user (Rootless mode)&lt;/a>
中可以不作为root用户运行，在Docker Engine v20.10发布&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在ubuntu上可以直接运行&lt;code>dockerd-rootless-setuptool.sh install&lt;/code>或下载运行&lt;code>curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com/rootless | sh&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>但是在wsl2中存在问题，要使用&lt;code>dockerd-rootless-setuptool.sh install --skip-iptables&lt;/code>禁用iptables检查，运行后提示成功：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ dockerd-rootless-setuptool.sh install --skip-iptables
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">[&lt;/span>INFO&lt;span style="color:#f92672">]&lt;/span> systemd not detected, dockerd-rootless.sh needs to be started manually:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>PATH&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>/usr/bin:/sbin:/usr/sbin:$PATH dockerd-rootless.sh --iptables&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>false
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">[&lt;/span>INFO&lt;span style="color:#f92672">]&lt;/span> Creating CLI context &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;rootless&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Successfully created context &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;rootless&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">[&lt;/span>INFO&lt;span style="color:#f92672">]&lt;/span> Make sure the following environment variables are set &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>or add them to ~/.bashrc&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>export PATH&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>/usr/bin:$PATH
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>export DOCKER_HOST&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>unix:///mnt/wslg/runtime-dir/docker.sock
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>但是DOCKER_HOST不合理，docker没有被安装在wslg中，运行&lt;code>docker stats&lt;/code>失败&lt;code>Rootless mode&lt;/code>在wsl中不可用&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://stackoverflow.com/a/48957722/8566831"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>How to fix docker: Got permission denied issue&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/linux-postinstall/"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Manage Docker as a non-root user&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="配置wsl2-docker自启动">配置wsl2 docker自启动
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>wsl2没有systemd，不能使用官方教程
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/linux-postinstall/#configure-docker-to-start-on-boot"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Configure Docker to start on boot&lt;/a>
，只能使用service启动。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>配置sudo在运行service命令时不会请求密码&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code class="language-bassh" data-lang="bassh">echo &amp;#34;$USER ALL=(ALL:ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/sbin/service&amp;#34; | sudo tee -a &amp;#34;/etc/sudoers.d/$USER&amp;#34;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;p>然后在&lt;code>~/.zshrc&lt;/code>中启动docker&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>service docker status &amp;gt; /dev/null &lt;span style="color:#f92672">||&lt;/span> sudo service docker start
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://blog.csdn.net/weiyi556/article/details/78980139"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>sudo visudo 退出保存&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://askubuntu.com/a/878705"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Execute sudo without Password?&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="docker更换国内镜像">docker更换国内镜像
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>配置文件启动Docker,修改&lt;code>/etc/docker/daemon.json&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;registry-mirrors&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: [
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;http://hub-mirror.c.163.com/&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> ]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>修改保存后，重启 Docker 以使配置生效。&lt;code>docker info&lt;/code>查看&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ sudo service docker restart
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ docker info | grep -i mirror
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> Registry Mirrors:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> http://hub-mirror.c.163.com/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>